        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;School Safety Drill Research Act of &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;b&gt;2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Department of Education to enter into an agreement with the National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine to study and report on the mental health effects that may result from a lockdown drill or active shooter drill in elementary and secondary schools.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
